<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink150-kilavi">
        vāyilvēṇṭiya tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ vāyiṉmaṟuppāḷ colliyatu </p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the heroine to the confidante who wanted entry [for the hero], as one who refused entry [to him].
  </p>
 </div>      
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink151">
<l>veḷḷāṅ kurukiṉ piḷḷai cetteṉak</l>
<l>kāṇiya ceṉṟa maṭanaṭai nārai</l>
<l>mitippa nakka kaṇpō ṉeytal</l>
<l>kaṭkamaḻn tāṉāt tuṟaivaṟku</l>
<l>nekka neñca nērkal lēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>To the man from the ghat, in which the nectar of the Neytal flower</l>
          <l>Like naked [=open] eyes being fragrant, does not end,</l> 
        <l>As the wader with an inexperienced gait that went to see,</l>
        <l> - Since the hatchling of the white wader died - </l>
        <l>Stamped on [that young one].</l>
       <l>I am not in agreement [with a/my] heart that has become soft.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
